data.description: Over 1 acre with a 3 bedroom 2 bath home close to town and other amenities! Hard to find property at this price point. The property is mostly level and useable with many options. Full two car garage, and bonus room. The Seller is will to negotiate a credit to the Buyer for anything they like; rate buy down, upgrades it is the Buyer's choice! This is a must see property.
